url.description: URL on which to serve the content

hidden.description:
Do not output for this specific Route

It can still be output with --include-hidden, as it is needed to declare the route in API Gateway or any other internal documentation

model.description: If defined will link to the model schema instead of a generic Object

dynamicSessionKey.description: If specified will verify the signature match the key store in session

public.description: Define if the object is publicly readable

name.description: Friendly user name of the key

permissions.description:
Retriction on URL to apply to the key

Split per method, each item of the array contains a regexp to validate the url used

whitelist.description:
If defined the key is only usable from these ips

Support of DNS is not yet ready

webda/apikey.description: Api Key to use with hawk
webda/apikey.title: ApiKey
